# Scope Boundaries (MVP Guardrails)

## Source Of Truth
- If this file conflicts with [CLAUDE.md](../../CLAUDE.md), **CLAUDE.md wins**.

## In Scope (Now)
- Import Center hardening
- Core entity consistency
- Output Center quality gate + traceability
- Template/version binding
- Basic identity + auditability
- Postgres-backed persistence

## Out Of Scope (Now)
- Generic AI chat page
- Autonomous multi-step agent write-back
- Full OCR automation pipeline
- Heavy BI analytics suite
- Complex org/permission matrix
- Native mobile app
- Large third-party integration expansion

## Rule
- For out-of-scope requests, create extensibility points only.
- Do not implement heavy features in current sprint unless explicitly approved by user.

